## Run CA_census_tract_dataclean.Rmd first.
## This analysis uses the CAcountytract output of that file. 

```{r census-tract ID summary}

library(tidyverse)

CAcountytract %>% 
  group_by(COUNTY_NAME) %>%
  count(COUNTY_NAME) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=n)) + geom_boxplot()

```
